Author: httpram
Text: i’m pretty much around your year yeah, thank you so much ): ❤️ im almost out for the year too, i wish both of us luck 🎊

Author: isaezraa
Text: I’m assuming you’re in high school? I know how you feel, and it’s so awful that you have to go through this. I’m in year 11 and I’m so fucking done with everyone here, but I keep telling myself that theres only 6 terms left and then I’m free. Teenagers are awful so please don’t take anything assholes say to you seriously, I know its cliché to say this but it seriously is just a projection of their own insecurities. Everything will be better when its over. Whats really helped for me is focusing on blocking everything out and focusing on doing my own shit.
